column16: Bryan Petersen triples (2) on a line drive to left fielder Jordany Valdespin.   Greg Dobbs scores.    John Buck scores.    Gorkys Hernandez scores.
Gorkys Hernandez singles on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Jordany Valdespin.   Greg Dobbs to 3rd.    John Buck to 2nd.
Nick Green pops out to first baseman Ike Davis in foul territory.
Greg Dobbs doubles (6) on a fly ball to right fielder Mike Baxter.
